d\n\n  trash [<messageId> ...] [flags]\n    Move messages to trash\n\nWrite\n  send [flags]\n    Send an email\n\n  track <command>\n    Email open tracking\n\n  drafts (draft) <command>\n    Draft operations\n\nAdmin\n  settings <command>\n    Settings and admin","cwd":"/Users/louishyman/.openclaw/workspaces/maxwell-workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775994512485}}
